47
00:05:39,370 --> 00:05:43,630
"To Annihilate the Straw Hats!
Legendary Assassins Descend!"

48
00:05:56,410 --> 00:06:00,420
PUNK HAZARD THE REMAINS OF THE
FIRST AND SECOND LABORATORY

49
