53
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:16,890
I hope this Master guy will just
come clean about those children.

54
00:06:16,890 --> 00:06:19,600
If he doesn't, I will force him to.

55
00:06:19,930 --> 00:06:24,410
I'll shove my finger into his nose
and make his back teeth rattle!

56
00:06:24,410 --> 00:06:26,780
Franky, please don't talk!

57
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,910
All right! Let's go now!

58
00:06:30,450 --> 00:06:32,640
Good luck!

59
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,860
Take care!

60
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,870
By the way,

61
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:41,320
why is he sleeping, too?

62
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:49,220
It's me.

63
