We just took care of three
of them for starters.

64
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:53,600
What?

65
00:06:54,150 --> 00:06:55,860
Pirate Hunter Zoro.

66
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,290
Cat Burglar.

67
00:06:59,140 --> 00:07:00,640
Soul King.

68
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:06,110
